{"tid":1053180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8旬婦忘帶鎖匙 驚動(73歲）兒子及（40歲）孫女開門爆打鬥同惹官非","createTime":"2019-03-08T22:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T23:23:00.000Z","uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac0edc550301120be51d6d5a7c7dd0cfcd8a2f8","tid":1053180,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:48:47.000Z","msg":"香港仔鴨脷洲大街一個住有三代的家庭，昨日（7日）晚上11時許，竟因瑣事演變成「家變」，事緣姓張（88歲）老婦由外返家，因忘記帶鎖匙，無法開門，驚動屋內的姓袁（73歲）兒子及40歲孫女開門，豈料3人為此而爭吵，各不相讓下，大動干戈。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，經調查後，因3人俱有動手打鬥，全部拘捕，其中父女涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，老婦則涉普通襲擊，她因手部受傷，需送院接受治理，警方仍就案件進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港高齡化的情況原來已經咁嚴重"},{"pid":"84eae39b20a78679a6bdba8d67767e733e8e02fc","tid":1053180,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:50:29.000Z","msg":"七十年前已經有十四歲媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d067f82de9d193d11ea0506ebb637144996c5a3f","tid":1053180,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84eae39b20a78679a6bdba8d67767e733e8e02fc","tid":1053180,"uid":42448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:50:29.000Z","msg":"七十年前已經有十四歲媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:56:49.000Z","msg":"唔係親生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedb007221ac6e2300ae8409775e69cde29505ee","tid":1053180,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T23:23:00.000Z","msg":"仆街啦 漏左銀包係屋企<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cpPnrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cpPnrT</a><br />\n<br />\n係唔係巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}